      <title>My new album Water Songs: Danish summer, Zealand. In between taking care of my d...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DNvvGqFWEc0/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/539425354_18520521691001293_2819945520543499703_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=111&amp;ig_cache_key=MzcwNjM4ODE3NTE4MDU5MTU0NQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=-UeP4y42ZsMQ7kNvwHQwUZl&amp;_nc_oc=AdrnDKzWPl8IAvKV5KqvmH6rGrYoXXMju-SYqQNlKSg1U_K74-gpTWAF0NwF4EBf25k&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=HHoR5gEtWpWsVwCMOYdrQw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afx9kXkOkpqDTIB9G9Qvo_jx-5Uk6Tz5TU-PXDMvpu1YoA&amp;oe=69C8DFE1" alt="Instagram billede fra @andersxrhedin" /></p><p><strong>@andersxrhedin</strong></p><p>My new album Water Songs: Danish summer, Zealand. In between taking care of my daughter I would sneak out and record rain, tumbling rocks, the surf at night or in the morning, forest sounds, wind sounds. And I added instruments. The water related sounds + synths, piano, effects is this new album. Out on @capturedtracks</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/539425354_18520521691001293_2819945520543499703_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=111&amp;ig_cache_key=MzcwNjM4ODE3NTE4MDU5MTU0NQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=-UeP4y42ZsMQ7kNvwHQwUZl&amp;_nc_oc=AdrnDKzWPl8IAvKV5KqvmH6rGrYoXXMju-SYqQNlKSg1U_K74-gpTWAF0NwF4EBf25k&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=HHoR5gEtWpWsVwCMOYdrQw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afx9kXkOkpqDTIB9G9Qvo_jx-5Uk6Tz5TU-PXDMvpu1YoA&amp;oe=69C8DFE1" alt="Instagram billede fra @andersxrhedin" /></p><p><strong>@andersxrhedin</strong></p><p>My new album Water Songs: Danish summer, Zealand. In between taking care of my daughter I would sneak out and record rain, tumbling rocks, the surf at night or in the morning, forest sounds, wind sounds. And I added instruments. The water related sounds + synths, piano, effects is this new album. Out on @capturedtracks</p>]]></content:encoded>
